S.FORM: Cliff Barker nalecuhan i Atlanta, Georgia, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. Cliff Barker i 1949 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 5 ku uwac, namapili' tu nu Washington Capitols putiput. 2 bulad 15 demiad, 1921 a mihca, Cliff Barker, miunduay. (mapatay i 1998 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
